OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779296759
OL,3,CTorrential rain and flooding kills 12
OL,4,Cin China as thousands evacuate home
OL,6,FAt least 12 people have died and
OL,7,Fthousands of others have been forced
OL,8,Fto evacuate their homes after
OL,9,Ftorrential rain and floods hit parts
OL,10,Fof China.
OL,12,FA cumulative rainfall of 339
OL,13,Fmillimetres was recorded in Shimen
OL,14,FCounty, of Hunan province, central
OL,15,FChina, within a 24-hour period ending
OL,16,Fat 7am on Monday, Chinese official
OL,17,Fnews agency Xinhua reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
