OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779296759
OL,3,CTorrential rain and flooding kills 12
OL,4,Cin China as thousands evacuate home
OL,6,FOne of the county's towns received a
OL,7,Frecord-breaking rainfall of 240
OL,8,Fmillimetres within just a few hours,
OL,9,Fit said.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FMore than 19,000 people from the area
OL,17,Fhave been relocated due to flooding,
OL,18,Fand a rescue operation is underway for
OL,19,Fpeople who have been reported missing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
