PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779296759
OL,3,CTorrential rain and flooding kills 12
OL,4,Cin China as thousands evacuate home
OL,6,FIn nearby Hubei province, some streets
OL,7,Fhad been turned into rivers by the
OL,8,Fintensive rain and inflatable boats
OL,9,Fhad to be deployed to help stranded
OL,10,Fresidents get to safety.
OL,12,FThree people had died and four others
OL,13,Fwere missing in the province as of
OL,14,FTuesday morning, Xinhua reported.
OL,16,FThe cities of Jingzhou and Zhijiang
OL,17,Fsuspended work, school, business
OL,18,Foperations and public transport, with
OL,19,Fauthorities in Jingzhou activating a
OL,20,FLevel III emergency response for flood
OL,21,Fcontrol.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
