PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1779296759
OL,3,CTorrential rain and flooding kills 12
OL,4,Cin China as thousands evacuate home
OL,6,FState broadcaster CCTV reported that
OL,7,Ffour people had died and five others
OL,8,Fwere missing in Guizhou Province in
OL,9,Fsouthwestern China due to the rain and
OL,10,Ffloods.
OL,12,FIn some areas, houses flooded, roads
OL,13,Fwere damaged, and communications were
OL,14,Fdisrupted, with one area evacuating
OL,15,Fmore than 3,700 people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
